                        <interp inst="t18370130-name-171" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY JOYNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Mr. Blaylock, and was in the shop—I saw the gentleman take the handkerchiefs out of the prisoner's pocket—they were given to the policeman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370130-name-172" type="witnessName">
